Package net.minecraft.world.entity.ai.behavior

Interface BehaviorControl<E extends net.minecraft.world.entity.LivingEntity>

Type Parameters:
E - The type of entity that the behavior runs on.
public interface BehaviorControl<E extends net.minecraft.world.entity.LivingEntity> 
Represents something that can control a behavior's running state.
